languages.text: Кровь продолжит литься на Веабосе-6, но взирать на схватки гладиаторов отныне будут не богохульные ксеносы, а рьяные слуги Вольного Торговца, усердным трудом заслужившие толику развлечения.

languages.text: Blood will continue to flow on Vheabos VI, but now the gladiator fights will be watched not by blasphemous xenos but by zealous servants of the Rogue Trader whose diligent toil has earned them a bit of entertainment.

traits.locale_text: Blood will continue to flow on Vheabos VI, but from now on, gladiator fights will be watched not by blasphemous xenos, but by zealous servants of the Rogue Trader, who have earned a bit of entertainment with hard work.
